title: 'Criminal Minds' Season 11 Spoilers: The BAU Team Will Go to Detroit in Episode 5 and A. J. Cook Will Return from Maternity Leave in Episode 7
text: 'Criminal Minds' Season 11 Spoilers: The BAU Team Will Go to Detroit in Episode 5 and A. J. Cook Will Return from Maternity Leave in Episode 7 Friday, 23 October 2015 (20 minutes ago) The BAU team heads to Detroit to find out who kills several victims and paints the scene as a street graffiti. Meanwhile, Dr. Lewis struggles to balance work and her personal life.
